  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Much sought her for her wise counsel and looked up to by everyone who, who certainly met her and by many who have only known her by reputation.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] She also [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I think bequeathed to me, who [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] at a certain point in her life was probably the closest [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] to her because my father had been out of the house since 1939, having gone to America.",
      "word_count": 52
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And during those days, I had to assume the, the role of the man of the house, so I became, I think-- I'm sure that my sisters feel that way about their respective relationship-- but I think I became the closest collaborator of hers and closest friend of hers because there were areas of life that she didn't have to share with my sisters but had to share with me.",
      "word_count": 70
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I became something of a helper and breadwinner in the last three, four years before the Holocaust.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, my father finally-- because it became physically dangerous for him to attempt to continue in the United States-- I mean in Hungary-- finally permitted himself to be persuaded by my mother to go to the United States.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Ostensibly, he came to represent Hungarian wine and liquor export to the World's Fair in 1939 at New York but with the intention of what he considered to weather the storm.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Maybe it'll take six months or so.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He had been to the United States before.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my mother, who sensed the-- way, way back-- the inevitability of the tragedy that was lurking at us and at the Jewish community of Hungary, was begging him for years to go to the United States.",
      "word_count": 37
    }
  ],
